        ],
        "name": "A MODERN FRAGRANCE HOUSE",
        "settings": {
          "copy": "<p>Conceptual Luxury Fragrances. Inspired by Horses. </p><p>Maison d’Etto is a luxury fragrance house rooted in authenticity, intentionality, and the equestrian spirit.</p><p>Each scent is inspired by a real horse that changed a life — capturing invisible languages, deep emotion, and the quiet power of movement. Crafted in collaboration with world-renowned perfumers, our fragrances are raw, personal expressions of memory, identity, and the beauty of imperfection.</p><p>Where scents are not just worn but lived. Thoughtfully created to inspire moments of connection, reflection, and well-being, each fragrance nurtures the human spirit, awakening deeper meaning — one moment at a time.</p><p>Authentic, genderless, and modern, Maison d’Etto invites you to connect with scent in a more intimate, profound way — one that honors individuality and champions sustainability, story, and soul.</p>",
          "link": "/pages/about",
          "main_thumbnail": "shopify://shop_images/HP-About-01_eacbda23-64c5-40c8-83e1-e9e35097f765.jpg",
          "main_thumbnail_caption": "<p>Maison d'Etto draws inspiration from art, architecture, design and the modern equestrian lifestyle.</p>"
        }
      },
