      "utility-content": {
        "type": "utility-content",
        "settings": {
          "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
          "headingMobile": "Shipping & Returns",
          "content": "<p>Maison d'Etto ships to the continental United States (excludes Puerto Rico, Guam, American Samoa, Alaska, and Hawaii). We are currently not able to deliver shipments to P.O boxes or APO/FPO addresses, military states, U.S territories, or International locations. </p><p>We ship orders within 3 business days of the day the order is placed. We must ship perfume via ground transport according to the law, so shipping time can take 1-7 days with our carrier, USPS or UPS (usually 1-2 days within NY-Tristate area).</p><p>DELIVERY DELAYS & LOST PACKAGES<br/>All purchase orders come with the opportunity for you to protect your purchase at checkout with Route shipping insurance. We are not responsible for carrier delivery delays and lost packages. If a package is lost by the carrier, and you have not opted in Route insurance, we will do our best to assist you and the carrier to find it but cannot make any guarantees. Please email <a href=\"mailto:info@maisondetto.com\">info@maisondetto.com</a> with any additional questions regarding shipping and delivery.</p><p>RETURNS & EXCHANGES<br/>If you are interested in returning an eligible, unopened, unused product with packaging fully intact within 14 days of receipt of your order, you may initiate a return request by emailing <a href=\"mailto:info@maisondetto.com\">info@maisondetto.com</a> and referencing your order number. </p><p>The customer is responsible for the costs of return shipping. Once the product is received back to our warehouse, we will refund the purchase amount minus a restocking fee of $15. Returns will only be accepted the original packaging and labeling are fully intact and the product is in salable condition. Refunds for returned merchandise will be made within two weeks of the return of the product to the original credit card. </p><p>If you have a quality concern such as breakage during transportation or malfunction within a 14-day period following delivery, please take a photo of the issue in question and send it with your order number and description to <a href=\"mailto:info@maisondetto.com\">info@maisondetto.com</a> and we will happily proceed to resolve the issue. </p><p>Items purchased online at <a href=\"http://www.maisondetto.com\">www.maisondetto.com</a> will not be accepted in retail store or pop-up locations or any third-party locations carrying Maison d'Etto merchandise.</p><p>Items purchased in a retail store, pop-up location, or third party location are not available for return directly to Maison d'Etto.</p><p>The Discovery Set and customized sample sets are final sale, and not eligible for return.</p><p>ADDITIONAL QUESTIONS<br/>For any other questions, please contact us via email at <a href=\"mailto:info@maisondetto.com\">info@maisondetto.com</a>. Please reference your order number within your email to help facilitate the process. We are available Monday through Friday, between 10:00AM and 3:00PM Eastern standard time.</p>",
          "isShippingEnable": true
        }
      },
      "product-shipping": {
        "type": "product-shipping",
        "settings": {
          "copy": "<p>Please see below for our Shipping & Return policies:</p>",
          "text": "<p>Standard shipping will be calculated at checkout. By law, fragrance must be shipped via ground transportation, because of this please allow additional time for it to reach your destination. We hope you are fully satisfied with your order and experience, however in the case that a return needs to be made. You are able to return unopened, unused product with packaging fully intact within 14 days of delivery. There will be a $15 restocking fee and you will be responsible for the costs of return shipping. If the product is damaged we will address on a case by case basis. For additional information on our policies please review our shipping & returns page. Additional questions? <a href=\"/pages/support\">Contact us</a>.</p>"
        }
      },
