      "about": {
        "type": "about",
        "settings": {
          "heading": "About",
          "image": "shopify://shop_images/ABOUT-01.jpg",
          "title": "MODERN LUXURY SCENTS \nTO INSPIRE CONNECTION",
          "contentLeft": "<p>What does ETTO mean?<br/></p><p>The word ETTO is born from Ethics and Motto — a quiet echo of the beliefs we carry with us, constant and unshakable, no matter where we stand in life. It also gestures toward the phrase Each To Their Own — a reverence for individuality, self-expression, and the freedom to feel deeply and define beauty on one’s own terms.</p><p>At Maison d’Etto, we don’t impose meaning. We offer a sensorial framework — a series of olfactive portraits — through which you are invited to explore your own truths. </p><p>Here, fragrance becomes a form of inner dialogue, a return to self, and a space for memory, movement, and discovery.</p>",
          "contentRight": "<p>What does ETTO mean? </p><p>The word ETTO is a combination of Ethics + Motto. ETTO represents the core truths and beliefs carried despite where you are in life or what you are going through. ETTO also stands for \"Each To Their Own.\" We are a brand that refuses to dictate values and beliefs to the wearer but empowers them to explore what ETTO uniquely means. </p><p>What does Etto actually mean? Derived from the words <em>“Ethics”</em> and <em>“Motto,”</em> ETTO reflects the core beliefs that guide us — truths that remain constant, no matter where life leads. </p><p>At Maison d’Etto, we don’t dictate what to believe or how to feel. Instead, we offer a canvas — through fragrance — for you to explore and define what <em>Etto</em> means to you. Our scents are designed to evoke emotion, stir memory, and connect you to something deeper and uniquely your own.</p><p>It also stands for <em>“Each To Their Own,”</em> a phrase that captures our belief in personal freedom, self-expression, and individuality.</p>",
          "enable": true
        }
      },
