          "text_H3nHTx": {
            "type": "text",
            "settings": {
              "hidem": false,
              "dis_img": false,
              "adjust_img": false,
              "image_width": 660,
              "img_position": "above",
              "image_crop": "default",
              "image_crop_location": "center",
              "title": "Fragrance is the invisible bridge between who we are and who we are becoming.",
              "all_caps_heading": false,
              "fs": 16,
              "fsm": 16,
              "lh": 1.2,
              "adjust_text_ls": true,
              "text_ls": 1.2,
              "tbm": 30,
              "text": "<p>There is a red thread that runs through the dust of the arena, the damp morning air, and the silence of the stable. It is the pulse of the horse—a life force that mirrors our own.</p><p>I have always found that horses bring a profound understanding to our lives without the need for words. They do not speak, yet they tell us everything. They are the ultimate mirrors; they see us before we see ourselves, reflecting our energy back to us with startling clarity.</p><p>At Maison d’Etto, this connection is my source. I do not paint with colors; I paint memories and lived experiences with these animals into our fragrances. We do not simply compose scents; we transcribe moments of profound connection into olfactive storytelling.</p><p>As we enter the Year of the Horse, we are returning to this source.</p>",
              "text_override": true,
              "text_fs": 12,
              "text_fsm": 12,
              "text_lh": 1.6,
              "btntxt": "",
              "btnurl": "",
