              "lh": 1.2,
              "adjust_text_ls": true,
              "text_ls": 1.2,
              "tbm": 30,
              "text": "<p>THE ARCHETYPES OF THE SPIRIT</p><p><strong>EIGHT MUSES. EIGHT INTENTIONS. WHICH REFLECTION IS YOURS?</strong></p><p>To choose a fragrance is to choose an intention. In the stillness before a single note is composed, there is a frequency—an energy held by our muses. These spirits do not demand our attention; they simply wait for us to recognize ourselves in them.We invite you to look past the scent profiles and listen to the metaphors. Forget the notes. Close your eyes and see which olfactive narrative leads you home.</p>",
