              "tbm": 0,
              "text": "<p>There is no singular way to inhabit these scents. At the heart of Maison d’Etto is <em>Etto</em>—the belief that your experience is your own, a unique imprint born from your own lived moments.</p><p>There is no right or wrong; there is only resonance. We encourage you to explore, and then to return. Our perspectives shift with each passing day, month, and year. You may be surprised by what resonates when the light, the perspective, or the seasons change.</p><p>Let your intuition be your guide, and allow your preference to evolve as you do.</p>",
